{"tid":2008683,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人類大命運同香港現況","createTime":"2020-05-09T08:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T16:13:32.000Z","uid":6005,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd9c863ec173c12fdc6fb700fcd9832c8992b37","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"咁本書入而講人類比起其他生物進步，就係因為大規模而靈活既合作性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好像螞蟻規模大但靈活性不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而狼就靈活性強卻規模不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個就係人可以統治大量動物既原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而我大有撚頭，將呢個推廣到依家，點解香港人有二百萬人卻得不到想要的結果?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />POPO只有三萬人為何卻能處於上風?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n規模黎講，我地一定係足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁樣即係靈活性不足，用番人類大命運呢本書黎用例子，係1913年既俄羅斯，三百萬既上流階級點解可以統治到一億八千萬農工?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係最後卻在十月革命時被兩萬三千既共產黨支持者所推翻?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係靈活性分別<br />\n我地依家要做既野唔係去獲得中間派支持，唔應該為左民心，要思考既應該係如何最大化靈活性，如何讓支持者有效合作?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似呢排既和你sing咁，佢地就正正加強左靈活性而取得勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話大游行呢D冇用，佢係一個展示我地規模既好方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但追悼會呢個行為卻有些不智，因為第一靈活性不足，班popo一定一早知你地會過黎，而第二點就係規模上不大，難聽D講，同送頭冇咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解要一個月一次呢而唔半年,一年一次呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，日程表呢樣野又間接削弱左和你sing同和你lunch 之類既靈活性，我覺得應該用作大規模遊行上比較好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴絲有冇咩睇法一齊辯明下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:預左比人話係分化撚同熱狗，所以自認自己係分化撚同熱狗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a56f26d218f47089dc97c1788005cf7b9888040","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f9a6024f5568f942e5fafbed8d82a71fc362bb","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4364ecc112a510e298b53eb9aaa97ac6940d4f","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:17:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"342a41c69df3f79169c301769cbde082329996ab","tid":2008683,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:19:24.000Z","msg":"同意，我覺得悼念活動可以以網上形成舉行，唔好限死自己。"},{"pid":"a197691cf483fe017cf8841bf4af52b659dbf4c7","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:46:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f00950e813ef1bf5ba908b7a1f9a9da47cbd83ad","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:52:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cb557ad89c886a797ac5d0013693e4700b8ca473","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:43:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a8eb45331b28bb23ec2279134ba5ab8761261a1b","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e5c0746e6dc785f941dcdf5688b6b6cd04d97a07","tid":2008683,"uid":150216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"仲要有故事unite 整個hk identity"},{"pid":"0eeacb50a2741a84e588162dca7ed4ea14d0004a","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"50cdb6747f9bef4dbf53e441cfe19b20783c976f","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7df10b8be3c40026b267e3cd8fd46f486161185a","tid":2008683,"uid":174285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"個人認為其實香港人的確具有一定靈活性，之前遊行或者所有衝突已經睇得出，但係所有嘢已經去晒樽頸位"},{"pid":"3808a8bf470cd67184c807dbee9668ad5cf141e8","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"62e218b382a2b4b1bca9cf9a5a1bdee0db50a0b6","tid":2008683,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}